{
  "logNo": "223818135886",
  "title": "셀프달력만들기, 점보포토 포토달력으로 간편하게",
  "date": "2025-04-03",
  "labels": [
    "상품 소개"
  ],
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8ec4116-97d1-4a7e-9220-6b0cca51c47f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a58ae7a-f235-44e3-97d7-03c9b0a42a7c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-003b415a-213c-4fb6-bd3c-fde458880265\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"내가 고른 사진으로 만드는 감성 가득한 맞춤 달력\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd25403e-2a33-4cd7-9458-cf024ccfa0a3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2d3c7a76-7311-47da-a517-82714e591ba1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-229291d8-78ca-4fb9-9cde-c44505d3b386\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2e02c2e4-b61a-4f3e-8258-ef9528d93133\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cde5c45c-c6bf-41d8-8eac-2647626fa90e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">매년 새해가 되면 어김없이 필요한 것이 달력입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fc039567-0e49-4c61-970a-2c988d763cae\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-54ed3fcd-2b18-4e06-9a8d-863baa1ca1ff\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-98837f0c-6606-4bba-8c61-bab6e40be49d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2939b771-6905-493c-ac6d-a7266be541dc\" style=\"color:#000000;\">하지만 시중에 파는 달력은 디자인이 마음에 들지 않거나, 집안 분위기와 잘 어울리지 않을 때도 많습니다. 반복되는 기업 로고, 전형적인 이미지, 아쉬운 종이 재질까지.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7667adff-d713-42f0-a9c3-0358aeb71d30\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-96e8e546-4500-4fb6-95ea-243b55682a67\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1b9ec245-7501-45ca-9bdb-182ca5486ee4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0579e31c-5b81-4952-b3d3-ac94141cdcaa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-38434148-058b-4654-9c42-1a5eb3d44b0b\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-855d26cc-293e-43bc-bf01-fa8cd2f5262d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b267d5b4-b0dd-4913-bde3-23c479cbab98\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-64a3105b-693e-4739-8eb2-53f59f5ab5d7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>그래서 요즘은 '셀프달력'을 찾는 분들이 점점 늘어나고 있습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-acb0b2e4-713d-4504-8567-ae28daa0e2e9\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-86035853-56f9-45fd-9ecd-a573ee833c80\" style=\"color:#000000;\">내가 찍은 사진으로 직접 제작하는 포토달력은 감성도 살고, 인테리어 소품으로도 손색이 없기 때문입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7b31d8c6-fbd9-4d72-8737-b524d4d4e11e\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c3ce4ff8-3682-4c58-b55a-58b879729e39\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0948d350-6c39-40b8-8a03-6c80e2a779b6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-62dec679-1ea7-48e3-bcc1-80207e2ab34e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">특히 점보포토 포토달력은 누구나 간편하게 만들 수 있으면서도 완성도 높은 퀄리티로 많은 분들이 매년 재구매하고 계십니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2421a79f-e201-4f6f-a042-056b0acfbfbf\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4f2b8f75-d066-45b7-9b95-8b851949daa4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e49a65a7-1be6-4db0-8fee-27b262de77dc\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1f145f4e-2450-4f39-bee8-19f667ab4e50\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>오늘은 점보포토 포토달력에 대해서 소개해 드리겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-43e4ab83-1486-47ab-93aa-e26755ab925f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-69a7ed09-bc4b-45ce-9e2a-cc6d14a9582c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a0624bc5-b5c3-4fbf-9d59-03a439c73724\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e343b2d-79e1-4d16-9624-8b243bd58c2c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c04b9d57-7184-4492-bd52-b891ddb0914b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>먼저 \"한 해가 시작된 지 1분기가 지났는데, 왜 필요할지\" 의문이 드실 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-884b2176-ff94-4c08-93b1-52e0cd7427cd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-70f82940-6907-4a90-a4a1-0c4b14756d04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d5e1d1ea-9b7a-45d6-bb3a-d69b02d4de5d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ed5fc2f6-d328-4fe0-864f-299a935552c4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-6b19af37-98fa-40b8-bf1b-e7baa68dbfb8\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fbae0d85-d8ae-4c7f-a867-348c3258648c\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">점</span>보포토 포토달력은 원하는 '시작 월'부터 달력을 만들 수 있습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5b6341ca-264a-4e67-b3c6-9565d37c211f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7e98caa1-1252-4e2b-873f-8d9c7be0fe74\" style=\"color:#000000;\">1월이 지나도, 3월부터 시작하는 달력이 필요해도 언제든 제작할 수 있답니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3555fa83-ed1d-496b-8b2c-cbff9b1cd9d0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-32e87c21-0384-42ab-9546-dde6e2ab7953\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2e5760d3-a4a5-4c35-8299-bdb5528511dd\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-873317e3-4127-401b-b366-35a3e629ae99\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>게다가 기념일을 자유롭게 입력해 해당 날짜에 특별한 표시를 남길 수 있어, 생일, 기념일, 기부 일정 등 소중한 날들을 잊지 않고 관리할 수 있습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b290e01a-8729-409f-b8d6-65683792999c\" style=\"color:#000000;\">그래서 아이 등원 시기나, 커플 기념일, 새로운 프로젝트 시작을 기준으로 세상에 하나뿐인 맞춤형 달력을 제작할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f6864aca-1d53-43af-8427-dbfef8542195\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1f5aaff0-3c78-4e7c-933c-e21411ed4516\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8a98b31d-27f6-47d2-a710-459ea5404c29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc9e844d-4a4c-4aed-b11c-968da4ba2ee3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a8c55520-2304-4887-a1a4-d76745cf399d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b2d0a456-bace-40d6-9543-35e4ad68692e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-4a543dc4-47cb-4695-bd0b-062cccb801f9\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5dc05e64-d56b-4a13-90db-185cec42ad31\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">달</span>력은 단순히 날짜만 보는 용도가 아닙니다. 하루하루의 순간을 더 따뜻하게 만들어 주는 감성 아이템이기도 합니다</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1f3d4f27-93f8-430c-b3c5-d396eedbbc6b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">. 특히 소중한 사람과의 추억이 담긴 사진으로 매달 다른 페이지를 꾸며보면, 달력이 하나의 감성 앨범처럼 느껴집니다. 매달 넘길 때마다 떠오르는 기억, 사진 한 장에 담긴 웃음, 눈빛, 배경까지 모두 의미가 된답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a4353915-2604-4596-b401-f40a5646ae46\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-851bb5d0-0cce-49a4-9d39-80003f2d861d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-3c46c5c4-479f-45b5-8fc1-4db6b5e35afe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a12bb792-dbcc-42ed-aa9b-0ddd4ad47dda\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b0e7c9c7-0ade-411e-8bcb-7729e6bc4f23\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"그럼 포토달력 어떨 때 제작하면 좋을까요?\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6c8ce7c-d233-4221-8a5f-60fe64c2ec55\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b7ca8fc6-5396-4914-91a1-e401066c3965\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-addcbf2d-a3c9-4aea-bd89-28734ae6bf50\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7c05f013-6af1-4dc7-a119-c032091896e2\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-9c559a6c-9424-49a4-b8c6-e426fca30930\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-70bab961-9c8c-4a5c-b63e-c34c8392d2cf\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">아</span>이의 성장기를 기록한 사진으로 월별 달력을 만들면 매달 자라나는 아이의 모습이 그대로 담깁니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-997c3651-1b5e-473c-a9ce-809aff665086\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u>아기의 백일, 첫 걸음마, 돌잔치, 첫 생일 같은 시점을 한 장 한 장에 담아 매년 아이와 함께 넘겨보는 재미도 있습니다.</u></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cf9868a7-1e51-4f76-aa6c-47bd6d2f48e8\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b6426077-911e-4842-adf0-6c836d6ff8c6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9618b9b8-7471-4d86-a020-06c762c41f89\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c7823e55-ddbd-4e13-a4bf-7f0f696258e1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0080c7a8-c040-46de-856b-ab0abe52eda7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>연인과의 추억 사진으로 제작한 커플 달력은 기념일 관리와 감성 인테리어를 동시에 만족시켜 준답니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4363d17f-1eb8-4a3e-879f-38b04beefffb\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6db6987a-9592-4419-ba73-a78aef0520c1\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64308d05-bd6c-4bc9-8005-41688e93470f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-35ec972f-227e-4bc1-a688-b6d3ab171a95\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b0322a22-4b13-4cad-9b7d-3fefd52da83e\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8f691c86-ebf1-4337-abb1-9f0b58821be6\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-268dc065-6b46-4bb7-8073-90a15bc8a9f2\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d3a7c2c9-ec86-4a6b-8a49-f2dda6d31158\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">친</span>구들과 여행, 가족 행사, 반려동물 일상, 프리랜서나 크리에이터라면 나의 작품과 기록을 담은 포트폴리오 달력도 만들 수 있습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f3cb9c87-5a1a-479c-92ea-8e2f9df24540\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-751b5bbc-ad61-45b3-914a-f8e878108c06\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-85087aa1-8347-483d-9d3a-a298c45f2882\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-690ef064-2279-4a86-9b22-2c19027cf71a\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">무</span>엇보다 특별한 건 군대 간 남자친구에게 선물할 수 있는 '기둘력' 달력입니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-16db30d3-9ac0-49e5-b9c4-84f4a7a25e3a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">복무 기간에 맞춰 사진과 기념일을 넣을 수 있어 기다리는 시간 동안 마음을 따뜻하게 해주는 의미 있는 선물이 된답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-28973c86-1314-4f75-8eb9-a5b926016def\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-756c9214-6863-4947-9ac2-a38b1043c636\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-9ae849dd-0efb-4f9e-9d11-632d68564c31\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eaa2e477-dc99-4e06-9502-0051b77b3aef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2935e563-b15b-4cc3-8b4d-b37c4749a8de\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"많은 분들이 점보포토 포토달력을 다시 찾는 이유는 바로 '이것'입니다.\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9e608d4e-e3ee-41c6-9ead-e673b80c9bf5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6fe59ab5-dfdd-4572-bae0-7a066a659ea3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-35e844d7-0bd3-4243-94c6-2ca3b3f2cc04\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d54df2c2-f943-459b-afff-c8f12dc45d65\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-a3d109f1-0c54-4dc3-8d71-2b43c0498de5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9e2236e5-b345-4ea5-92ae-9ed0d9b932c7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">점</span>보포토 포토달력은 고급 인쇄 장비로 출력되어 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-10be0503-cd06-4d34-b995-7e69678d5ef1\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>선명한 화질과 풍부한 색감</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d3339fbc-9af8-469e-8dca-a6f747afce05\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>을 보여준답니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-16247e05-e1ac-4f11-82d8-81372e601924\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>후지필름 QPDP 인화지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2625d44e-d40f-4864-bc71-99f2a6e57c9e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>와 퀄러티가 높은 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f557647d-deb7-4126-a307-360d5820d6c2\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>랑데뷰 190g 용지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b50355d8-b09f-4a6f-bfa0-6d881872fe74\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>를 사용하여 인쇄 품질이 뛰어납니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a07d8ee8-0da4-40e8-9217-57e5e16af5ea\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>불투명 보호필름(아스테이지)와 트윈 코팅 스프링 제본</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-bbb672d2-a288-4d3a-93ca-38aa8b71bac8\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>으로 내구성과 완성도를 모두 챙겼습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92ef0734-c9d8-4aa0-86aa-b278a00fa947\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3ee2a055-cfde-4778-8f5c-fff835fbee32\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bafb5d4e-771e-465e-8d63-40afe3a7b352\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-099f4053-260f-4699-9473-c9bdd0016dea\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-95c89411-0258-4c76-b9ef-69f577e7f8b4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d5173a55-596d-4560-af71-f8176e05d159\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">색</span>감 보정과 밝기 보정 기능도 편집기 내에 기본 제공되므로, 누구나 전문가처럼 깔끔한 달력을 완성할 수 있답니다</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-232c073d-7f96-455b-aea9-cba44a6d40cc\" style=\"color:#000000;\">. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-46cd38fa-d6b5-493d-9d12-7dffbd0b219a\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u>특히 사진에 따라 어두운 부분을 살리거나 선명도를 조정할 수 있어, 일상 사진도 훨씬 고급스럽게 표현할 수 있습니다.</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a0748f5d-ef80-464e-af82-185c3e11dafc\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6b2d548c-ed4d-4de9-916a-a18c11ef101e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-b105c7be-7997-4c71-a842-a5d2a132e0ff\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359fb656-e1b9-48f5-a293-58a9f9c17ea1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7205fb13-9ba5-4c25-b7c9-07709d9f53de\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"점보포토 포토달력 제품 종류도 다양합니다.\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-27dde7f4-7bf9-4a1e-9525-09c2c47da238\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-077a38bb-e7e0-488f-8e6b-201ce091397b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0a400a94-9c08-465e-847a-9c7fefe95c27\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e74522ce-0543-4fff-8c03-146ec9a55e0f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-3478b53e-f95d-4b81-8ebf-c6eaa92390c1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-068c825f-8cec-4b24-8a61-f628e525ef7d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">탁</span>상형 달력은 표지 1장과 달력 12개월 분량(24p), 에필로그 1장으로 구성되어 있습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-dca14597-81f8-446e-8589-1dfd44bd38eb\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>크기는 미니, 티니, 베이직, 라지까지 네 가지 사이즈로 제공됩니다. 삼각대 색상도 블랙, 와인, 블루 중 선택할 수 있습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-42c4c81e-faa1-4691-bad3-791d8e77354d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">깔끔한 디자인과 튼튼한 삼각대 덕분에 책상 위에서 안정감 있게 사용 가능하고, 회의실이나 사무실에서도 활용하기 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b45d5ce7-2d5b-4dfe-8c6c-4fa9457e8a7d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3393866b-5bd4-401e-b844-fd935661e7d3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f3403a8-24b5-4ec3-81fe-7da35d5a0bc3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1798c749-23e4-4dd4-a42f-b3a31858909c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3dec2420-e6de-4251-b98f-19b226aff3f7\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-190d15b5-5f2e-44bb-8d0a-b0d0017528d6\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-322d2dd0-1992-4147-a69f-2c26eea3a6eb\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-05a3bec2-2021-4a0a-95e3-ed5e0dfc3c3c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">벽</span>걸이형 달력은 베이직, 라지, 원피스 사이즈가 있고 A3 사이즈는 숫자가 크고 멀리서도 잘 보여서 인테리어용으로도 인기가 많습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7dca4ff8-2cd9-4183-939f-b7f11387a15b\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>거실 벽, 주방, 아이 방, 현관 옆 등 집안 곳곳을 꾸미기에 좋고, 분위기에 맞는 사진을 선택하면 공간이 훨씬 따뜻해 보입니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-93508c06-0383-4c0d-a8db-c4a6186d82ce\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 특히 가족사진이나 여행 사진, 아이의 일상 사진 등을 넣으면 벽에 걸어두는 것만으로도 기분 좋은 추억이 살아납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e06ce19a-0343-4df7-a63b-920919f7e54c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f5da6faf-efee-4738-b82b-605a23a88f9e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7c8ede07-e796-42b4-8a26-8c7b5acaf275\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b61cbf0e-f6d5-459a-916b-6171651afa60\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-31beadbd-c68b-4fc8-80df-ed0ce0b467e7\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6fbf8296-3691-42f2-bd32-122bb5d0d684\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-bbd375bb-b9be-48b7-a928-74c8ec04ade5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-00a572c0-852f-4147-ad23-95fad6bc0e18\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">기</span>둘력은 군 복무 기간에 맞춘 특별한 달력으로 육군, 해병대, 해군, 공군, 사회복무요원까지 각각 다른 페이지 구성으로 제공된답니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c850ff59-a907-41ec-b640-2cf182218bd5\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>육군은 18개월, 해군은 20개월, 공군과 사회복무요원은 21개월 분량으로, 표지 1장과 1개월 예고 페이지, 에필로그까지 알차게 구성되어 있습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2cc21893-b63d-4cf4-a2ec-d391b829c485\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2b9b389a-b5b7-44a9-8aa9-de3d299d6ee5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ff672856-301a-4c34-8e85-a294b3d833f2\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5152533d-33b8-4200-86a8-fada9c867eaa\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fddbb4f8-439b-43f8-a3ff-6d4067f8c89b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">매달 보고 싶은 사진을 한 장씩 넣고, 기념일을 미리 표시하면 복무 중인 연인이 달력을 넘기면서 기다림을 견디는 데 큰 힘이 되어준답니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-60f71a77-f3fb-4dec-a07f-db209895ab3b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u>실제 구매한 고객분들은 \"기다리는 남자친구에게 선물했더니 너무 감동하더라고요\"라며 만족을 표현해 주시기도 했답니다.</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-573e7e26-4908-4724-a05c-22a0895427ff\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-66b3768e-afb5-4d15-a720-440ad12e6ef0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8559029a-29fc-4741-950e-173e6e7bfb95\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5d7b571c-2c63-471f-ae39-5f574ee55107\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-564c1fa9-d854-4e19-9681-ba63a3e5c6c8\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9018e62f-921b-4a12-bd0b-9df4eee5db5d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-c1006a06-d15d-4dbd-885a-85c2d2ca14f4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b17fcd0c-36ad-403a-81bb-7ed01ad367b5\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">이</span>외에도 그림쟁이 옥철이와 제휴하고 있어서, 예쁜 옥철이 일러스트 달력을 완성본으로 만나보실 수 있습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c0524e7d-7746-4855-8b6c-493fe8084f40\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-eb1b87eb-0f41-43eb-9fd0-e807bc6b25b7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7bc5cd27-fbc5-4846-a80d-8eb8fec2db53\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73e87a82-d923-4ad9-99c6-b4020fe97562\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7574367a-8945-4d6a-bba0-bd848540bc3a\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"점보포토에서는 포토달력을 제작하는 방법, 정말 쉽습니다.\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-925ee8d5-492c-44ea-865a-5c988e8ce125\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bfa37cd-97ec-4c5a-8f14-d795e919d5db\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3175494b-c8f2-408b-8409-f1dca98c85e3\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5ab1403c-a0cc-4ab0-a21c-d6ebe4bc2013\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-77dcbf40-5bc7-4a60-8e5a-31ff7742fd84\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-29844e35-bca4-424b-ba28-47db00dbdfad\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">점</span>보포토 웹사이트나 앱에서 포토달력 카테고리를 선택한 뒤, 원하는 달력 종류와 사이즈를 고릅니다. 이후 점보포토 편집기를 실행해 준비해 둔 사진을 드래그해서 원하는 위치에 배치하면 됩니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f905b42f-1bb0-403d-a3b2-b67d8db10014\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>사진 배치뿐만 아니라 텍스트 추가, 기념일 표기, 문구, 아이콘 등 다양한 꾸미기 기능도 제공되어 감각적인 연출이 가능하답니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5754eeec-dfc6-44a0-98ea-72b564501db4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b9888319-4b1b-46cb-b97d-294a26230886\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-14029e64-1bbc-4b0c-a7f4-5670d06eb0a5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3281bf4b-474b-4742-9538-c2af9c438e0b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2144f22a-7a0f-49b8-8c57-9a7b1e656ec9\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c6f7ad0c-aa04-4aae-a86c-4d6d0707393d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-75dc451b-37de-48e4-8acf-c75a0160b296\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-792e2a5b-74f7-4585-99de-4ffae98c87f3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">시</span>작 월을 자유롭게 선택할 수 있어 3월, 5월, 9월 등 언제든 내가 원하는 시점부터 달력을 제작할 수 있습니다. 편집이 끝나면 장바구니에 담아 결제하고, 안전 포장 후 빠르게 배송되니 금방 받아보실 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7709380f-0783-4386-a296-55db032d81e6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3d6e0de5-1861-4e2c-8dcc-02feea4d8473\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-be3aa3df-dd4a-41f7-8e7a-c2aafb7402d8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b172a761-1bdc-41bf-a063-48ea2c18d48f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ae1b8f69-dd87-41a2-bfaf-26e19d0a10be\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"실제로 만족해하시는 분들이 매번 이용하고 계십니다.\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-317022b0-c890-4600-8368-689c4c36624c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-779bfdd6-dd46-4669-afe0-1da5366eb96a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f78ae991-7a52-427d-8d00-0a2cd9e51c96\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>\"사진 품질에 좌우하기는 하지만 너무 예쁘고 선명하게 잘 나왔어요\", \"사진 쪽에는 날짜가 없어서 사진으로 둘지 달력으로 쓸지 고민이 되네요\"처럼 사용자의 솔직한 후기가 많습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-156b0d24-0d24-44dc-b22a-eb8988899372\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-dcd36634-f54e-41ad-9361-d22ee7448047\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2305b69a-43e2-46a1-9167-0ccdbea20710\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8811a2b1-b324-4834-88f3-e57af45adebe\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>급하게 요청한 제작 일정에도 빠르게 대응해 \"예쁘게 잘 나와서 무척 만족스럽다.\", \"주변에 소문 많이 낼게요\"라는 반응도 있었습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-09fc1fed-1e6d-40e5-adb7-4c5897945dda\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fd34dd05-c9f6-4a40-8ad0-23a5c237765e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6335d8b7-915f-4c33-94a6-7ed1d887de63\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/013.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-868945af-480f-4b26-a13a-7cd7a0497ad1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d123bd31-c220-4179-9475-53e983ae20c0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5eab9bbe-f519-4267-893a-d1c1e9308c61\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-8c778291-724d-46f3-a909-791bf2867e29\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-94bcc092-141e-489a-b540-488a655be12f\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">선</span>물용으로 제작해 \"받은 분이 너무 좋아해서 저도 기뻤다\"라는 경험담도 주셨습니다. 매년 직접 가족 달력을 만든다는 분부터, 은행 달력만 쓰다가 처음으로 사진 달력을 만들어 보니 뿌듯하다는 후기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-563a9c25-5a41-48e5-804b-75d86aed529d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">까지, 점보포토 포토달력은 감성과 실용성을 모두 만족시키는 제품으로 자리를 잡고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d68148d0-2b27-47cd-88f4-2b2de9f323a7\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c4e5ef62-9faa-4048-b249-22f75e8e80ab\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fb2dea2a-869e-4ef2-af09-9ba32565548d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223818135886/014.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00bec0ce-df79-4522-acbf-41fc8121fe8d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dabcc2da-0f4b-46a1-bac3-e5ca6def3b0a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-eba78718-6768-4c91-945d-6a715c76c5d3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-b23a4e21-1f56-454e-adfe-526a78b8105f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8828ad2a-1637-444e-b8fb-18e9f761f33f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">하</span>루하루를 더 특별하게 채우고 싶다면, 달력부터 바꿔보는 건 어떨까요? 단순히 날짜만 확인하는 용도가 아닌, 감성까지 담아낼 수 있는 셀프 포토달력. 점보포토에서는 그 모든 과정을 쉽고 간편하게, 그리고 만족스럽게 도와드립니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ef314ba5-bf31-415a-b8c2-b8925f07295a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9974a2a5-74e9-4316-badb-ebd1f677f200\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ab67a7bf-3a4f-41e9-98e4-acda1c8e175e\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a49901d3-21b6-4f00-b9d9-aba0e9dacc52\" style=\"color:#000000;\">나만의 사진과 디자인으로 완성한 맞춤형 달력은 집 안 분위기를 바꿔주고, 소중한 사람에게 전하는 특별한 선물이 되어줍니다. 지금 바로 점보포토에서 당신만의 셀프달력을 시작해 보세요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-284b36b6-6128-4599-aa91-4f3f1623be83\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4c71d2e1-e76e-4d5b-bca1-48f23a44d7c7\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-4d41ca57-f1e1-49ae-85ad-9d2c1a52f5f5\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-833edb02-978e-4963-847c-1d0f93bc04e9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3a085a24-7fde-438a-9cda-5f137c947748\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-65a15392-3808-44f5-a6ab-d428a1c1a20d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
